<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ881104-0141 </DOCNO><HL> Who's News: Sony Corp. </HL><SO> </SO><CO> SNE WNEWS </CO><DATELINE> SONY Corp.  </DATELINE><TEXT>   Sony Corp. of America named M.H. Chaffin vice president of a new division, Optical Storage Systems, which will coordinate the Japanese electronic company's optical-storage peripheral products and systems operations and CD-ROM publishing services in the U.S. He remains vice president of the Advanced Technology Group. </TEXT></DOC>